responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "034B7A404069247EB785249DFA8A7660", "Yon farmhold is called The Daragal Estate. I was told that their great well has historically been a source of pure, essential water - and the fecundity of the soil here speaks for itself! I purchased shares in this endeavor before I struck out from Lionhold, and expected them to be up and running by the time I arrived, but alas!")
